Lab 1 DoS Traffic Characterization in CORE (hping3 + Wireshark)

This lab uses a CORE-emulated multi-subnet topology to generate and measure DoS-style traffic against a web server, validate impact on an HTTP client, and produce ISP-ready filtering guidance using Wireshark display filters and IO Graphs.

## Environment / Topology

- **Client:** `10.0.1.20/24`
- **Server:** `10.0.2.20/24` (HTTP on port `8000`)
- **Attackers:**  
  - Attacker1 `10.0.4.20/24`  
  - Attacker2 `10.0.4.21/24`  
  - Attacker3 `10.0.3.20/24`  
  - Attacker4 `10.0.3.21/24`
- **DNS Server:** `10.0.1.22/24`

